verbose_text: Comparison of IL-2 production by Jurkat-PD-1 OST and Jurkat-PD-1 OST SHP-2 - clones in response to Raji + SEE showed that in the absence of PD-1-PD-L1 engagement, the lack of SHP-2 had no measurable effect on TCR-CD28-induced IL-2 production (XREF_FIG C, left panel).
evidence: IL-2 production by Jurkat-PD-1 OST  and Jurkat-PD-1 OST  SHP-2
